`socketio` is a translator designed for creating socket ports through the
filesystem.

This is supposed to replace [[netio]].


# Source

[[source_repositories/incubator]], socketio/master


# Usage:

For example:

    $ cat < ~/tmp/socketio/tcp/ftp.gnu.org/21


